-- Zhongjin Gold to Pay 0.15 Yuan Cash Dividend Per Share, Give Bonus Stock
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-04T23:35:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-04/zhongjin-gold-to-pay-0-15-yuan-cash-dividend-per-share-give-bonus-stock.html

          
          
             Zhongjin Gold Co. will pay a cash
dividend of 0.15 yuan a share, according to a statement to the
stock exchange.  
 The company will also give shareholders 0.8 bonus share for
each share held, according to the statement.  
